<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>١٤٧ -<span class="c5"> وَسَأَلْتُهُ عَنْ مَالِكٍ الأَشْتَرِ:</span> يُرْوَى عَنْهُ الْحَدِيثُ؟<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ:</span> لا.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>١٤٨ -<span class="c5"> وَسَأَلْتُهُ عَنْ عَبْدِ اللَّهِ بْنِ الْكَوَّاءِ:</span> يُرْوَى عَنْهُ الْحَدِيثُ؟<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ:</span> لا.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>١٤٩ - وَسَأَلْتُهُ عَنْ يَزِيدَ بْنِ المهلَّب؟<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c5">فَقَالَ:</span> بَصْرِيٌّ صَاحِبُ فِتْنَةٍ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>١٥٠ - وَسَأَلْتُهُ عَنِ الْحَجَّاجِ؟<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c5">فَقَالَ:</span> كَانَ قتَّالاً للأنفس.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>١٥١ -<span class="c5"> وقال أبو طالب:</span> سَأَلْتُ أَحْمَدَ: عَنْ مَنْ قَالَ: لَعَنَ اللَّهُ يزيد بن معاوية؟<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c5">فقال:</span> لا تَكَلَّمْ فِي هَذَا.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c5">قُلْتُ:</span> مَا تَقُولُ؟ فَإِنَّ الَّذِي تكلم به رجلٌ لابأس به،<span class="c5"> وقال:</span><a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>